reviewText: WOW, this is FANTASIC.  Performances from the 1950s through the 1990s by Patti Page.  There is no questiion she was and still is the BEST.  Her record sales are over 100 million.  15 gold singles and 4 gold albums.  Had the industry awarded platinum discs back in the 1950s, she would have about 33 platinum discs and 45 or so gold records.  Unbelievable accomplihment.
